    <div class="py-2">
      <text class="text-lg">
        Currently a Software Engineering student at the <b>University of Waterloo</b>.
        Interested in artificial Intelligence, cybersecurity, and software engineering.
        Reach me at <b><a href="rsaid@uwaterloo.ca"> rsaid [at] uwaterloo.ca</a></b>.
      </text>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8">
      <a class="btn" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/rawsabsaid/" target="_blank"> Let's connect!</a>
      <a href="/cv" class="btn btn-outline ml-5">
        View my resume
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div>
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold mb-2">My last projects {"</>"}</div>
